    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*简介</strong></h2>身为月上派六骑士的兔克失去了记忆，拿起螳刀再次游历月窟吧！你将体验到：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15个各具特色的Boss<br></li><li>50个功能各异的道具和技能<br></li><li>1个主线剧情和5个支线故事<br></li><li>6张地图和超过70个场景<br></li><li>各种有趣的小游戏<br></li><li>以及更多！</li></ul><br><strong>《只兔：不灭的勇者》</strong>使用国产引擎<strong> -唤境- </strong>制作，感谢<strong> -唤境- </strong>提供的支持和帮助：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/85f8df595c8741cda6b54cf6ec314e6f.avif?t=1737514536\" width=600 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*故事背景</strong></h2>月窟中的生物们从未见过月亮却为月亮而痴迷。<br>为了寻找月亮，人们分化成了认为月亮在天上和认为月亮在地底的月上月下两派。<br>身为月上派六骑士的兔克，将要为了昔日的誓言拯救垂危的月上派。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*游戏特色</strong></h2><strong>- 硬核的战斗 -</strong><br>判断敌人的动作来进行闪避、格挡和进攻是游戏的核心。<br>主角将以脆弱的身躯和简单的招式去挑战强大复杂的敌人！当然也可以通过各类道具逃课…<br><i>（归功于我们的 程序兼美术 豆豆萌萌兔）</i><br><br><strong>- 丰富的玩法 -</strong><br>游戏内有大量的用处各异的道具供玩家收集，他们可能出现在月窟世界的任何一个角落。<br>同时有钓鱼、斗蟹、成就、矿场、炒股等乱七八糟周边玩法，可以在硬核战斗之余缓解一下紧张的气氛。<br><i>（归功于我们的 策划兼美术 豆豆萌萌兔）</i><br><br><strong>- 好看的剧情 -</strong><br>随着游戏进度慢慢恢复的兔克的记忆，了解兔克和其他六骑士的过往，并慢慢解开月窟世界的真相…<br>通过简单的漫画以及人物对话的形式来进行表达，简约而不简单。<br><i>（归功于我们的 编辑兼美术 豆豆萌萌兔）</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*画面展示</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/50980524ad09fba59eadbe6f7b190a45.poster.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/50980524ad09fba59eadbe6f7b190a45.webm?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/50980524ad09fba59eadbe6f7b190a45.mp4?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/6abf8b63538ce21fd4db1a8479291b2f.poster.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/6abf8b63538ce21fd4db1a8479291b2f.webm?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/6abf8b63538ce21fd4db1a8479291b2f.mp4?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-精通敌人的招式来进行精确的招架、翻滚和拼刀，每一场战斗都可能要受苦。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/30dfc921ac116ffa7fd92fddc738eb3d.poster.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/30dfc921ac116ffa7fd92fddc738eb3d.webm?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/30dfc921ac116ffa7fd92fddc738eb3d.mp4?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-获得的月魄可以提升自己的各项能力，通过精进的技术和搭配的技能来击败更强大的敌人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/228ad2d90cdc6236f8c6e9a053ae1d9d.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/3c66e6120be0fdce174ec4b0867815ee.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 /></span><br>-巨大的月窟有数个不同风格的地形及城镇，拜访他们来恢复兔克的记忆。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/8390ed746293e2dec2c503beffd71930.poster.avif?t=1737514536\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/8390ed746293e2dec2c503beffd71930.webm?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836030/extras/8390ed746293e2dec2c503beffd71930.mp4?t=1737514536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-还有我喜欢的乱七八糟的玩法。<br><br><br><i>*本游戏由 豆豆萌萌兔 耗费 1 年独立完成开发。<br>*本游戏内你能看见的所有美术素材皆由 豆豆萌萌兔 使用像素绘图软件 -aseprite- 耗费 2500+ 小时独立完成绘制。<br>*本游戏内bgm由 豆豆萌萌兔 在多个无版权背景音乐素材网站上精心挑选。</i><br><br><strong>希望你喜欢这个游戏 0v0</strong>",
